{"tid":2101885,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[突發] 郭安發死咗","createTime":"2020-07-10T05:50:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T23:35:06.000Z","uid":31048,"like":12,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d7095eec5b855ab65cfd542a90afbb44830d12ff","tid":2101885,"uid":31048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T05:50:05.000Z","msg":"未?<br />\n<br />\nAIG前經理收賄千萬囚54月<br />\n更新時間 (HKT): 2007.09.06 00:00<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/oC7Pm8FiqyUrfeSvoQyAKS_i7R0=/802x1118/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SOBFRY224CDOSD3VAT42DRIFQY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FoC7Pm8FiqyUrfeSvoQyAKS_i7R0%3D%2F802x1118%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSOBFRY224CDOSD3VAT42DRIFQY.jpg&h=71d5e883&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【本報訊】美國國際信貸（香港）有限公司（下稱AIGFinance）前旺角分行經理，收受共約1,000萬元賄款，向公司虛構一名村屋發展商以地皮或樓宇作抵押借貸，或將村屋誇大成西班牙三層高別墅提高貸款額，令發展商於9年內獲批2,278萬元貸款，導致公司呆壞賬達1,300萬元。前經理05年由美國引渡返港，早前被裁定兩項串謀收受利益及一項串謀詐騙罪成，昨在區域法院被判囚四年半，及賠償145萬元可追查到的賄款予受害公司。<br />\n<strong>51歲被告郭安發</strong>自90年起，向公司虛構一名村屋發展商以土地或樓宇作抵押貸款，或將簡陋村屋說成西班牙三層高別墅，以獲批出較高貸款額。<br />\n已無資產賠償<br />\n<br />\n90至99年間，發展商聲稱抵押6間元朗及八鄉的村屋，向AIGFinance取得2,278萬元貸款，被告共收1,000萬元賄款。<br />\n<strong>其代表律師昨指，郭於05年患上甲狀腺癌，治癒後患青光眼及高血壓，要定期覆診，至今已無資產可供賠償。</strong><br />\n案件編號：DCCC68/07"},{"pid":"145b0dbe8084035e7f428e73f1a826940175f5b4","tid":2101885,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T05:51:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />黑警"},{"pid":"1be5b70229c6d3719d19663cd9f0427ba8455cfb","tid":2101885,"uid":188310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T05:51:40.000Z","msg":"郭安發壽終正寢"},{"pid":"8a388fe404ad5c385e71f5d0076182c6e79cc017","tid":2101885,"uid":265646,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T05:51:59.000Z","msg":"郭安